story.text: Woke up with zero sickness today. All throat frog is totally gone - amazing.
Also had a really productive day working on the New Shape application. Read their historical pieces and nothing was similar to what I am proposing. Yay. I think I will submit pseudonymously.
Meeting Ben, Brittany, and the girls for lunch, Yay!!!!
